## Description

Introduces notes_browser, a Flask-based web application that provides a GitHub-style interface for browsing PR summaries stored in git notes.

Features:
- List view of all commits with PR summary notes
- Detailed view with formatted markdown rendering
- Code comment display with file context from commits
- Support for multiple git notes refs
- GitHub-style dark theme UI
- Author linking and @mention support

This complements the pr-summary action by making the stored PR data easily accessible and browsable without requiring git CLI commands.

